# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:12
translate spanish welch9_77b3956a:

    # "In Ms. Welch's class, I try to focus on my test, attempting to recall all the information that I had memorized while studying earlier in the week."
    "En la clase de la Sra. Welch, intento concentrarme en mi examen, tratando de recordar toda la información que había memorizado mientras estudiaba a principios de semana."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:13
translate spanish welch9_1d38c971:

    # "Ms. Welch walks through the class, looking to see how everybody is doing and watching out for any cheaters."
    "La Sra. Welch recorre el aula, echando un vistazo para ver cómo va todo el mundo y atenta a cualquier trampa."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:16
translate spanish welch9_92d9ffe5:

    # "When she passes by my desk, she slides a small note down in front of me."
    "Cuando pasa por mi pupitre, desliza una pequeña nota delante de mí."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:17
translate spanish welch9_67c479b9:

    # "She does it so slyly, not even looking down as she places it, never missing a step as she continues walking the room."
    "Lo hace con mucha astucia, sin siquiera bajar la vista al colocarla, sin perder el ritmo mientras sigue recorriendo el aula."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:18
translate spanish welch9_0e4d4622:

    # "I quietly unfold the note and take a look."
    "Desdoblo la nota en silencio y le echo un vistazo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:25
translate spanish welch9_95ec0fac:

    # "I look up again and see her standing by her desk, smiling at me."
    "Levanto la vista de nuevo y la veo de pie junto a su escritorio, sonriéndome."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:26
translate spanish welch9_00e23a96:

    # "She wants to talk to me. And gave me her phone number."
    "Quiere hablar conmigo. Y me ha dado su número de teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:27
translate spanish welch9_6bf4ecfb:

    # "I'll have to give her a call sometime soon, I guess."
    "Supongo que tendré que llamarla pronto."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:30
translate spanish welch9_af06cabf:

    # "Nothing else interesting happens the rest of the day, then I have to leave."
    "No pasa nada más interesante el resto del día, y luego tengo que irme."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:33
